subSubSection.paragraph:
Habitat.
Subtropical, broadleaf, evergreen, deciduous, submontane and bamboo forests and teak plantations. Depending on the region, the Capped Langur is sympatric with Phayre’s Langur (71. 
phayrei
) and the Nepal Sacred Langur (
Semnopithecus schistaceus
).

